Package: khaos
Type: Package
Title: Bayesian Sparse Polynomial Chaos Expansion
Version: 1.0.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Kellin", "Rumsey", , "knrumsey@lanl.gov", role = c("aut", "cre"),
           comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-2989-965X"))
Maintainer: Kellin N. Rumsey <knrumsey@lanl.gov>
Description: Implementation of the sparse Bayesian PCE approach of Shao et al. (2017). The algorithm can be very expensive for a large number of predictors, and so LASSO is used to restrict the number of basis functions which are given consideration. 
